To view the public IP of an instance, follow these steps:

1. Log onto Amazon EC2 console.
2. On the leading(Left hand) side of the page, under "INSTANCES" navigational header, select "Instances".
3. Select the desired instance.
4. At the bottom of the page, a menu appears with a tab navigational menu.  Select "Description" tab.
5. Alongside the "IPv4 Public IP" label is displayed the public IP address of the instance.
